EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\\\\\\\">18 to 25</span>tons per hectares.</li></ul><div><br></div>','<ul><li>Tolerate a wide range of soil types.</li><li><p class=\\\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\\\" style=\\\\\\\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:107%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\\\\\\\">Silty to sandy loam soils with
pH 5.5 to 7.0.<o:p></o:p></span></p></li></ul>','&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Filler Crops&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Tomatoes-&lt;/b&gt; Have similar soil and water requirements, also grow to a similar height, so
they wont shade each other excessively.&lt;b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Eggplant-&lt;/b&gt; Have similar cultural requirements.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Worst
