INSERT INTO "crops_list" VALUES (26,28,1,'Carrots','<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"text-indent:.5in\\\"><span lang=\\\"EN-US\\\">In the Philippines, a carrot is simply
referred to as \\\"karot.\\\" This term is widely used in markets,
kitchens, and everyday conversations across the country when referring to the
orange root vegetable.<o:p></o:p></span></p><div><br></div>','<p><b>Time of Planting</b></p><ul><li>Month of October up to February, Carrots are cool weather crop. So, it takes more water to grow. If you are providing proper water, it will grow soon.<span style=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"> </span></li></ul><p><b>Volume of Productivity</b></p><ul><li>4 to 8 tons per hectares.</li></ul><div><br></div>','<ul><li>Carrot prefers sandy loam to clay loam soil.</li><li>A pH range of 6.0 to 6.8 is recommended to ensure a good yield.</li></ul>','&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Filler
Crops&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Onions and
Garlic:&lt;/b&gt; Can help deter pests that might otherwise bother carrots. They do not
compete heavily with carrots for nutrients as they have different nutrient
requirements.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Radishes
(Labanos):&lt;/b&gt; Radishes are often used as a companion for carrots. They can help
repel some soil-dwelling pests.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Worst
Companion&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Celery:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;can
be a bad companion plant for carrots because it can attract the same pests and
diseases, including carrot rust fly.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Potatoes
ripen around the same time that celery reaches its full growing potential.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;

