</p><ul><li><span lang=\\\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\\\" style=\\\\\\\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:106%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\\\\\\\">2.5 to 4 tons per hectares.<o:p></o:p></span></li></ul>','<ul><li style=\\\\\\\"text-align: justify;\\\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\\\">Grow in sandy loam or
